(1)
1010 East 89th Street, at the N.W. corner of Lott's House Road, showing the house of R.S. Schenck; (it was also known as the Steve Schenck house). Building in the background, is No. 1019 East 88th Street.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, a rear view. Shown on the right, is No. 1019 East 88th Street.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3)
The same, a different angle. June 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
